{
  "stem": "21582.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If the Germans poked their bayonet in your bed, if you were found-- and if you were hiding, there you were found.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we-- it was a four-story building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So everyone in the row, in this one row, one on top of another, we put a, a wardrobe, Anne Frank style.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We put a wardrobe in front of the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of us in this building, we only stayed in one place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was in my friend, Janka's room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was her room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But all the, all the rooms were disguised by the closets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there we sat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we, we, we, all we could hear from, from behind the doors is when you click hear the screamings, and the slapping, and the kicking, and the shooting, and the screams.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and then the most, most petrifying thing was when they walked through each apartment, and you could hear their boots, or them leaning against the closet, the wardrobe, or moving-- looking inside the wardrobe.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That, that was just-- you know, that was just so, so petrifying because you were just a hair away from, from, from your hunters, from your assailants.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, then eventually you would hear the, the, the wailing and the noise.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It recede.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, you're always think-- oh, they are trapping us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is it safe to come out?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, then, then the real wailing came out because people were afraid to cry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when you heard these, these, these, these shrieking cries, these, these most heart-rendering screams, these outcries, then we knew that it was safe to step out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you slowly-- usually we, we would move the, the wardrobe slowly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Be careful, be careful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we would come out.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
